.. _changelog:

###################
Datarray change log
###################

The main authors of datarray are:

* Fernando Perez (FP);
* Matthew Brett (MB);
* Mike Trumpis (MT);
* Jonathan Terhorst (JT);
* Keith Goodman (KG).

********
Releases
********

* 0.1.0 (TBA)

  * Fixed bug in axis sorting leading to unpredictable errors slicing
    DataArrays;
  * Added 'any' and 'all' as reduction methods, fixing incorrect retention of
    axes with these methods;
  * Port to Python >= 3.3 in common codebase with Python 2;
  * Move from fperez personal github account to BIDS github organization.

* 0.0.6 (Wednesday November 10 2010)

* 0.0.5 (Friday October 8 2010)

* 0.0.4 (Wednesday October 6 2010)

* 0.0.3 (Thursday July 29 2010)

* 0.0.2 (Wednesday July 28 2010)

* 0.0.1 (Tuesday July 27 2010)

  * Initial release
